# CNN Edge Detection

This project demonstrates edge detection using convolution filters in TensorFlow.

## Overview

The notebook applies custom vertical and horizontal filters to a grayscale image to detect edges and visualize feature extraction.

## Concepts Covered

- Image Preprocessing
- Grayscale Conversion
- Convolution Operation
- Feature Extraction
- Edge Detection
- TensorFlow Basics

## Technologies Used

- Python
- TensorFlow
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Google Colab

## Output

The model generates:

- Original Image
- Vertical Edge Detection
- Horizontal Edge Detection

## Learning Outcome

This project helped me understand how convolution filters work and how Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) extract features from images.
